An OS/2-PM Editor Using MLE           by Brian R. Anderson

This directory contains the following (numbered listing) files:

   MAKEFILE.LS -- builds the program
   EDIT.HLS    -- base header (includes resource & ipf constants)
   EDIT.CLS    -- main(), ClientWndProc(), & subclassing
   EDLG.HLS    -- prototypes, etc. used by dialog box procedures
   EDLG.CLS    -- dialog box procedures and supporting code
   EFILE.HLS   -- prototypes, etc. used by file I/O procedures
   EFILE.CLS   -- file I/O procedures
   EDIT.DLS    -- linker control (module definition file)
   EDIT.ILS    -- help text
